          "tz": -360
        },
        "subject": "LU-9846 lod: Raise stripe count limit to 10K",
        "message": "LU-9846 lod: Raise stripe count limit to 10K\n\nThe overstriping feature makes it reasonable to use much\nlarger stripe counts than with a 1-stripe-per-OST limit.\n\nSo, this patch raises the stripe count limit to 10K.  This\nvalue was chosen because it's large enough for expected\nnext gen systems, but small enough that it still works on\ncurrent-gen clients without additional fixes.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I64b1d59d7d6ed9ff43a969afd6b911799b3dcc26\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
